    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed in mint condition, and that is a completely honest and accurate assessment \u2014 this car is as close to flawless as you will find on the used market. The exterior is genuinely pristine: the paint is deep, glossy, and free of scratches, chips, or blemishes, the body panels are perfectly aligned, and all glass and trim are spotless. The interior is equally impressive, with no wear on the seats, carpets, or dashboard surfaces \u2014 everything looks and feels as though it just left the showroom floor. Mechanically, the car runs and drives beautifully, with no unusual noises, hesitations, or warning lights of any kind. All features and systems \u2014 climate control, infotainment, power accessories \u2014 function exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a used vehicle that truly requires nothing at all.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition at $46,000, and that description is as accurate and honest as it gets. The exterior is truly exceptional \u2014 the paint is deep, rich, and lustrous with no visible scratches, chips, fading, or swirl marks. Panel gaps are tight and even throughout, and every body line looks as crisp as the day it left the factory. The glass is clear and free of chips or cracks, and all trim pieces, badges, and moldings are perfectly intact and properly fitted. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 the seats, dashboard, door panels, and headliner show no signs of wear, cracking, or staining. Every control, button, and feature functions exactly as intended, and the cabin retains a fresh, clean feel. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, with no leaks, corrosion, or neglected components. Mechanically, the car runs and drives with confidence \u2014 smooth acceleration, responsive braking, and no unusual noises or warning lights. The tires have substantial tread remaining and are evenly worn. This is a genuinely rare find: a vehicle that has been meticulously cared for and shows it in every detail. A serious buyer looking for the best available example will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 46000.0,
